<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Valentine's Surprise</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@400..700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: #ffebeb;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .envelope {
        position: relative;
        width: 200px;
        height: 150px;
        background: #d32f2f;
        border-radius: 10px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        cursor: pointer;
      }
      .envelope::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
        border-left: 100px solid transparent;
        border-right: 100px solid transparent;
        border-bottom: 75px solid #b71c1c;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .envelope::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        width: 0;
        height: 0;
        border-left: 100px solid transparent;
        border-right: 100px solid transparent;
        border-top: 75px solid #b71c1c;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .card {
        position: absolute;
        width: 160px;
        height: 100px;
        background: white;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #d32f2f;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
      }
      .card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
      }
      .open-button {
        margin-top: 10px;
        padding: 8px 15px;
        background: #d32f2f;
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 16px;
      }
      .open-button:hover {
        background: #b71c1c;
      }

      .container {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .container2 {
        display: flex;
        text-align: center;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      h1{
        font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>
      Happy Valentine's Day Sweetheart. Thank You for being a part of my
      journey. ðŸ’–
    </h1>
  </body>
</html>
